{"tid":1933867,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB又報假新聞？老屈富婆隻狗確診有武肺","createTime":"2020-03-19T14:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T22:03:45.000Z","uid":40466,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e619fbf7647b58eb106dbc08c31d1671a4659309","tid":1933867,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"TVB於2020年3月19日新聞報導中表示跑馬地富婆隻松鼠狗確診武漢肺<br />\n<br />\n1.由於主人(周巧兒)在狗隻死亡後拒絕進行驗屍，根本不能確定狗隻是因為確診武漢肺炎而死亡。<br />\n<br />\n2.衛生署由始到終沒有清楚表明松鼠狗是否確診<br />\n不停搬龍門,一時陰性,一時陽性。<br />\n而最後亦沒有清楚表示松鼠狗的血清究竟有無感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\nTVB作為香港主流電視媒體，於新聞報導中報導失實內容<br />\n有機會引起棄養潮，嚴重更可能把小動物殺害。<br />\n<br />\n而香港的動物保護法的漏洞十分嚴重，根本無法緝拿毒手。"},{"pid":"02cc577d804fe4d9ca6c68fef06d8d48ee668bd2","tid":1933867,"uid":40466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asSK4JM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasSK4JM.png&h=187fa863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d446853739061f2366cb70902f30a692272beacb","tid":1933867,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZwcu2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZwcu2X.jpg&h=af8e3c06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fa31d0d7d9dc1a3de9fbbe4407625d2b8bc7e66","tid":1933867,"uid":181797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T22:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}